- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper deals with a method for a robot to retrace a path in a changing environment.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the method involves visual perception and memory.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the approach involves training two neural networks end-to-end.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the method involves decision-making under uncertainty.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also relevant as the paper deals with controlling a system (robot) to follow a path.
